# Assets Securities Lending Program Amount

## identifier
de13189

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of securities available for arrangements that involve a transfer of legal ownership of securities between the holder and borrower, including the right for the borrower to on-sell the securities.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.SecuritiesLendingProgram.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.15
- period=instant
